      <h2>Reports, analysis and insight for media professionals.</h2>

      <p class="highlight">Medievärlden Premium is a subscription service that gives you better intel on the changing media landscape.</p>

      <div class="additional">
        <p>Medievärlden became an own entity in 2014. Prior to that they had belonged to and been funded by <a href="http://tu.se/tu-in-english/">The Swedish Media Publishers’ Association</a>. To be able to find new revenues they created the concept Medievärlden Premium. A new service aimed media executives that should be separated from their main news based and publicly open site.</p>

        <p>We designed and built this new service and provided the staff with a new administrative tool for managing all content, users and subscriptions. Users without a valid subscription can access parts of the content and functionality. The rest lies behind a paywall and users subscribe on a yearly basis.</p>
